      "duration_seconds": 1.0,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "I'll come back.",

      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "from_app": "Zoom",

    {
      "offset_seconds": 41.0,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 4.0,
      "speaker_label": "background",
      "text": "[Loud classroom chatter and shouting 'Bye!']"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 45.5,
      "event_type": "app_switch",

      "duration_seconds": 2.5,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "My name is Suzie, I'll be your tutor for today.",

      "event_type": "page_scroll",

      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1.5,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Okay, nice to meet you.",
      "speaker_name": "Suzie Baik"

    {
      "offset_seconds": 52.0,
      "event_type": "app_switch",
      "duration_seconds": 1.0,
      "from_app": "iOS Home Screen",
      "to_app": "Zoom",

      "duration_seconds": 0.8,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Um...",
      "speaker_name": "Suzie Baik"

    {
      "offset_seconds": 54.0,
      "event_type": "app_switch",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "from_app": "Zoom",
      "from_window": "Video Feed",
      "to_app": "Zoom",
      "to_window": "Sharing Screen",
      "details": "The student minimizes the video feed to show the 'You are sharing screen' interface."

    {
      "offset_seconds": 55.0,
      "event_type": "app_switch",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "from_app": "Zoom",
      "to_app": "iOS Home Screen",
      "details": "The student returns to the iPad home screen."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 56.5,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2.5,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Yeah, today I think we're just gonna introduce ourselves.",
      "speaker_name": "Suzie Baik"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 58.0,
      "event_type": "page_scroll",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "target_desc": "iOS Home Screen",
      "direction": "other",
      "details": "The student swipes left to the App Library again."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 60.0,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 4.5,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "I'm gonna go check on other students, but I'll come back to you, and if you have any questions you can always let me know.",
      "speaker_name": "Suzie Baik"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 63.5,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "speaker_name": "hannah"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 65.0,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 4.0,
      "speaker_label": "background",
      "text": "[Indistinct classroom chatter]"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 69.5,
      "event_type": "app_switch",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "from_app": "iOS Home Screen",
      "to_app": "Safari",
      "details": "The student taps on Safari/IXL from the App Library."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 74.0,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "text input field",
      "details": "The student taps the text box for t= to bring up the keyboard."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 75.0,
      "event_type": "keyboard",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "action": "type",
      "text": "6",
      "details": "Student types '6' into the answer box."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 76.5,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Submit button",
      "details": "Student taps the Submit button."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 77.0,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "description": "IXL displays 'Correct!' feedback."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 78.5,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 0.5,
      "description": "Screen sharing stops; view returns to Zoom gallery layout."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 79.5,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1.0,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Can you hear me?",
      "speaker_name": "Suzie Baik"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 81.0,
      "event_type": "inactivity",
      "duration_seconds": 41.0,
      "description": "Tutor sits silently, waiting for the other student (Mal) to respond. Mal's screen remains black."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 122.0,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 0.0,
      "description": "The participant name 'Mal' changes to 'Dawry' on the black screen."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 124.0,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1.0,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Can you hear me?",
      "speaker_name": "Suzie Baik"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 125.5,
      "event_type": "inactivity",
      "duration_seconds": 293.5,
      "description": "Prolonged silence. The tutor waits for Dawry. Dawry's camera remains off and no audio is heard. The tutor occasionally shifts posture or looks down but no interaction occurs."
    }
  ]
}
